Kwiki::HanConvert - Convert page display to simplified / traditional Chinese.

This Kwiki plugin make use of Encode::HanConvert, and adds [Simp] and
[Trad] on your toolbar, which conver your page display to Simplified
Chinese or Traditional Chinese on the fly. The conversion is
accomplished after page rendering, so the page content is not changed.

Cheers,
Kang-min "Gugod" Liu




